quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,"There has come upon man a period of time in which he was nothing worth mentioning."
  76,2,"We have created man from a mixed sperm-drop to put him to a test; then We made him able to hear, able to see."
  76,3,"We have shown him the way to be either grateful or ungrateful."
  76,4,"We have prepared, for the disbelievers, shackles and iron-collars and a blazing Fire."
  76,5,"Indeed, the righteous will have a drink from a goblet, blended with (a drink from) Camphor"